    <b>The following discs can be duplicated:</b>
    <p>- DVD-R: data/video/audio</p>
    <p>- CD-R: data/audio/video  </p>
    <p>
        You provide the master DVD or CD disc. Custom designed full color labels are printed onto the disc (no stickers to come off in your player!). 
        From text to photos to full color graphics and special effects...we do it all! Your discs will look great whether it's one copy or 500! We cannot provide jewel case paper insert printing. 
        The only printing we do is on the disc itself. For more information, read How AfterBurner Media Does It below.
        <br />
        <br />


        All discs are copied to high quality JVC/Taiyo Yuden hub-printable (white matte finish) CD-R or DVD-R discs.

    </p>
    <br />

