        <br />
    </p>

    <p>
        <b>Pricing is based on the following:</b><br />

        - Type of media(CD-R costs less than DVD-R)<br />
        - Time spent in label design<br />
        - Amount of ink required(is the label text only or a full color  photo or graphic) 
        <br />
        - Number of copies(generally, more copies = lower cost per disc)
        <br />
        - Deadline (projects needed within 72 hours will be charged a 25% 'rush' fee)<br />
        - Shipping (projects can be shipped via UPS, USPS or FedEx anywhere in the USA)
        <br />
    </p>

    <article>
