  These disks are fully printable from edge to center hub and come with a high quality white matte finish embedded into the disc (no stickers to gum up your CD or DVD players!).
  The white matte finish provides a high quality printing surface that will last for years to come.
  The HP 480i printer is capable of photo quality custom printing on the entire surface of the disc (printed case jackets and shrink wrapping are not available).<br />

